rdf:Description.lla:note: Col H - port she belonged to is given as N Quay next to the ships name, but CLIP does not have a the port of Newquay listed. There is a Dreadnought registered in Aberystwyth.
Col G - M Lloyd is written on the list but it is not clear what the abbreviation is for. There are 3 ships registered at Aberystwyth that it could be - Margaret Lloyd, Martha Lloyd or Mary Lloyd
